00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,620
Nice resume.

8
00:01:12,850 --> 00:01:14,750
You melted the coins
and sold them, right?

9
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,420
So Eun...

10
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:39,350
I have something to tell you
that I couldn't that day.

11
00:01:40,670 --> 00:01:43,150
This is the real me.

12
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:46,890
When my twin brother
Han Soo Ho went missing,

13
00:01:46,890 --> 00:01:48,970
I took over.

14
