It was a coincidence

15
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:03,040
but it was an opportunity for me

16
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,970
to get revenge

17
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:09,120
I could mess with the law, too.

18
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,250
But...

19
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:15,020
After I met you, I changed.

20
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:17,740
I may have lived my entire life
looking in the mirror

21
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:20,900
to see the reflection
of my mangled face.

22
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:24,400
I tried to leave halfway through.

23
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,120
But I couldn't.

24
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:29,270
I wanted to be with you,

25
00:02:29,270 --> 00:02:32,010
so I kept lying.

26
00:02:32,010 --> 00:02:34,460
If I became a good person,

27
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:38,540
maybe I would deserve
to like you. I dreamt of that.

28
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:46,530
I'm sorry I mocked the law.

29
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:49,100
I'm sorry...

30
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:50,990
I lied.

31
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:55,590
I'm sorry that I prayed

32
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,730
to be near you.

33
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:01,520
From Han Kang Ho.

34
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:08,230
♫ Tomorrow will come... ♫

35
00:03:08,230 --> 00:03:15,730
♫ In this darkness,
I'm looking for a path. ♫

36
00:03:15,730 --> 00:03:18,270
The gravity must be strong here.

37
00:03:20,230 --> 00:03:22,710
You must be my gravity, So Eun.

38
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:27,870
♫ In my heart full of pain ♫

39
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:34,890
♫ If you light it up with
your white light ♫

40
00:03:34,890 --> 00:03:43,250
♫ I want to dream once again ♫

41
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:47,910
♫ You are my only star ♫

42
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:56,290
♫ Someday, the darkness will break ♫

43
00:03:56,290 --> 00:04:02,410
♫ I will meet you at the end of this road ♫

44
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:09,280
♫ In my life, full of pain ♫

45
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:15,880
♫ With your warmth, embrace me ♫

46
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:22,200
♫ Shine on me ♫

47
