I like this.

48
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:31,890
You waiting for me with dinner.

49
00:04:31,890 --> 00:04:34,410
I can't believe you haven't
eaten until this hour.

50
00:04:34,410 --> 00:04:36,180
I have so much work.

51
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:38,820
I read more than a thousand
pages of paperwork today.

52
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:41,760
You picked something so difficult.

53
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:47,350
You took the bar exam
because of me, right?

54
00:04:47,350 --> 00:04:48,440
No.

55
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:51,750
You said you would become a judge or
prosecutor so you could try him again.

56
00:04:54,660 --> 00:04:57,860
But I never want to go through that again.

57
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,710
It felt like my soul was being ripped apart.

58
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:04,560
Have you forgiven him, Unni?

59
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,280
No.

60
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:10,610
I decided to believe in this
saying just this once.

61
00:05:10,610 --> 00:05:14,730
If you do something bad,
you'll be punished someday.

62
00:05:14,730 --> 00:05:20,290
If not in our generation,
in the next one, he'll pay the price.

63
00:05:20,290 --> 00:05:22,880
Is that enough for you? Really?

64
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:25,650
Yes.

65
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:36,270
He's in jail. For drugs.

66
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,160
I saw on the news.

67
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:41,210
He tried to weasel himself out,

68
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:43,120
but we tracked him down and got him.

69
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,060
You did?

70
00:05:44,060 --> 00:05:45,310
No.

71
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,880
Then who?

72
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:50,000
My judge.

73
00:05:51,730 --> 00:05:54,100
He's not a judge, but.

74
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:56,830
What's a judge that's not a judge?

75
00:05:57,970 --> 00:05:59,880
Exactly that.

76
00:06:02,210 --> 00:06:05,180
He wasn't a judge

77
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:10,320
but he was one.

78
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,170
This is salty.

79
