00:25:54,770 --> 00:25:57,550
How did you fool me so well?

317
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:59,130
I'm sorry.

318
00:26:00,430 --> 00:26:03,520
When you lie like that, isn't it scary?

319
00:26:03,520 --> 00:26:05,820
I was going to run away.

320
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:08,140
You couldn't because of me?

321
00:26:12,330 --> 00:26:14,630
It's my fault.

322
00:26:14,630 --> 00:26:18,380
I should have known when you told me
to summarize the main points.

323
00:26:19,530 --> 00:26:22,840
I should have suspected it when
you handed over all your rulings.

324
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:25,240
When you told me to fix the
Chinese character...

325
00:26:25,240 --> 00:26:27,480
I should have realized.

326
00:26:28,970 --> 00:26:30,540
But...

327
00:26:31,730 --> 00:26:33,870
thank you for finding my sister.

328
00:26:33,870 --> 00:26:36,300
Oh, it's nothing.

329
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:39,140
What else do I need to thank you for?

330
00:26:40,970 --> 00:26:43,660
I'm a trial researcher now.

331
00:26:45,150 --> 00:26:46,520
I know.

332
00:26:46,520 --> 00:26:49,090
I have a lawyer license too.

333
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:52,100
I have a culinary license.

334
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:54,270
Korean cuisine and Western cuisine.

335
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:56,220
Make me a meal, then.

336
00:26:57,610 --> 00:27:00,450
At least once. You promised.

337
00:27:01,630 --> 00:27:03,200
What do you like?

338
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:05,940
What are you good at?

339
00:27:07,130 --> 00:27:08,310
Anything.

340
00:27:09,370 --> 00:27:11,180
Then make me anything.

